quran[8{c,v,t}:
10,107,"agar Allah tujhe kisi museebat mein daaley to khud is ke siwa koi nahi jo is museebat ko taall day, aur agar woh tairay haq mein kisi bhalai ka iradah kere to is ke fazl ko phairnay wala bhi koi nahi hai woh apne bundon mein se jis ko chahta hai apne fazl se nawazta hai aur woh dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
10,108,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, keh do ke “logo, tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se haq aa chuka hai ab jo seedhi raah ikhtiyar kere is ki raast rawi isi ke liye mufeed hai, aur jo gumraah rahay is ki gumraahi isi ke liye tabah kin hai aur mein tumahray oopar koi hawala daar nahi hon """
10,109,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum is hadaayat ki pairwi kiye jao jo tumhari taraf ba zarea wahi bhaije ja rahi hai, aur sabr karo yahan taq ke Allah faisla kar day, aur wohi behtareen faisla karne wala hai"
11,1,"a l- ray farmaan hai, jis ki ayatain pukhta aur mufasil irshad hui hain, aik Dana aur bakhabar hasti ki taraf se"
11,2,ke tum bandagi nah karo magar sirf Allah ki mein uss ki taraf se tum ko khabardaar karne wala bhi hon aur basharat dainay wala bhi
11,3,aur yeh ke tum apne rab se maffi chaho aur is ki taraf palat aao to woh aik muddat khaas taq tum ko acha samaan zindagi day ga aur har sahib fazl ko is ka fazl ataa kere ga lekin agar tum mun phertey ho to mein tumahray haq mein aik barray holnaak din ke azaab se darta hon
11,4,tum sab ko Allah ki taraf palatna hai aur woh sab kuch karsaktha hai
11,5,"dekho! yeh log apne seenon ko morty hain taakay is se choup jayen khabardaar! jab yeh kapron se apne aap ko dhanpte hain, Allah un ke chupay ko bhi jaanta hai aur khulay ko bhi, woh to unn bheidoon se bhi waaqif hai jo seenon mein hain"
